Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Columbia space shuttle, 1981
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w9jw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Apr 1981
Boost for US as Columbia space shuttle makes first landing back on earth. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.